        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/community.signalusers.org/aku-stable/{size}/25198_2.png",
        "created_at": "2025-06-20T20:09:44.304Z",
        "cooked": "<p>On v7.45.3 stable, I took a photo inside Signal, sent to my story, but it’s stuck on Sending!<br>\nAt least there isn’t a crash loop. Maybe that only happens when attaching a screenshot from Google Photos?</p>\n<p>Debug Log: <a href=\"https://debuglogs.org/android/7.45.3/769c8c2b84c6e980940632dd6b789e1f12ee48e0eaa1290579e7c197122ac300\">https://debuglogs.org/android/7.45.3/769c8c2b84c6e980940632dd6b789e1f12ee48e0eaa1290579e7c197122ac300</a></p>\n<hr>\n<p>Edit: I tried posting a screenshot from Google Photos, it’s stuck on Sending. At least Signal isn’t stuck in a crash loop for 24 hours!<br>\nNew Debug Log: <a href=\"https://debuglogs.org/android/7.45.3/96d6cc5ee1d40ea94f5f6c788d4bde58a297a7f87156dbb38803d470a3a0fffd\">https://debuglogs.org/android/7.45.3/96d6cc5ee1d40ea94f5f6c788d4bde58a297a7f87156dbb38803d470a3a0fffd</a></p>",
