        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-username=\"braz29\" data-post=\"11\" data-topic=\"70182\" data-full=\"true\">\n<div class=\"title\">\n<div class=\"quote-controls\"></div>\n<img alt=\"\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/f475e1/48.png\" class=\"avatar\"><a href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/t/beta-feedback-for-the-upcoming-android-7-48-release/70182/11\">Beta feedback for the upcoming Android 7.48 release</a></div>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Impossible to post story on 7.47 it stays on sending mode without being actually updated. It was also the case on 7.46.</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://debuglogs.org/android/7.47.2/33d06ea0ba4dfb988e1645eaf04880c8fcc8043b9522af7f81ff0b2978368aab\">https://debuglogs.org/android/7.47.2/33d06ea0ba4dfb988e1645eaf04880c8fcc8043b9522af7f81ff0b2978368aab</a></p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>This seems to be the same problem I was facing.</p>",
